            <title>[LU-573] conf-sanity test_22: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_22 failed with 41</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-573</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When creating a file, it returned:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;LustreError: 20020:0:(lov_request.c:566:lov_update_create_set()) error creating fid 0x1 sub-object on OST idx 0/1: rc = -11&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;on the MDS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is recovery on the OST is not finished yet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
